Installation:

    cd ~/
    git init
    git pull git@github.com:chrispsn/config.git
    git remote add origin git@github.com:chrispsn/config.git

Adding stuff:

    git add .
    git commit -m "description"
    git push

Getting latest version:

    git pull

Submodules:

    http://chrisjean.com/2009/04/20/git-submodules-adding-using-removing-and-updating/
